reviews.text: Best conveyor-belt sushi in HK.
Everything was yummy! Only issue I had was , you had to have an app to order food.  So we ended up ordering food with the waitress .
Got a comfy seat without waiting at lunch time, it's just amazing in hustle and bustle Hong Kong!
Freah amd affordable sushi!
Food, delivery and services are good.  However, I felt uncomfortably thirsty afterwards.  Would it be because of MSG (味精)?

reviews.text: 실버코드 안에 있었다. 피크를 구경하고 출출해서 여기저기 둘러 보다가 들어간 초밥집이다 여기는 일단 2가지가 신기했다. 첫번째, 일반 회전초밥집 처럼 내가 먹고 싶은걸 기다려야하는게 아니라 내가 주문한걸 기차로된 접시로 바로 내앞까지 배달해준다는 점이다 두번째, 그 주문을 QR코드로 주문한다는점에서 놀랐다 가격도 저렴해서 가성비는 좋다
元氣一贯服務串串，叫客人落樓攞遮套再俾入去，真係大店先做得出，手卷的料也比我去其他分店特別少。
改了電話落單後，無了叫help功能，食物質素下降，問服務員問題答客人，再次帮陳令人卻步。
Best conveyor-belt sushi in HK.

result.name: Silvercord

reviews.text: Well equipped mall at the center of the shopping district. Have affordable shops as supposed to all the designer brands near by. Good places to eat inside, also affordable.

Silvercord is a shopping mall and office complex at the heart of Canton Road in Tsimshatsui. Its location is very convenient with walking bridge connected to the Harbour City, the largest shopping mall in Hong Kong. However, the mall seems a bit outdated in the interior decoration and the mall design. Always use liked a stepping stone to the nearest Harbour City from my point of view.

The concierge is really friendly always smiling and super helpful, he knows what service means, he took the pain to help me and not just by pointing in a vague direction, while welcoming me, and i felt like a guest in the building rather than an annoyance!!! Keep it up management you're doing great to have such awesome staff!!
Genki Sushi is the best addition to this mall
Good quality products. Attractive.
